0.34 -- Fri Jan 24 20:26:55 AST 2025

    [Significant updates since 0.31]
    - Updates for openssl 1.0 versions
    - Merged a minor Fedora patch for the Change log for correct UTF-8 names
    - Ah the good old days when SHA1 was good enough :-). RHEL, Fedora, SUSE
    - etc. have more secure configurations so many of the digests and curves
    - tested would fail - So test only a reduced set (based on Fedora 42+)

    [Change Log]
    - 47bea5b Increment version for a release
    - 0acc30e v0.33
    - 30872b6 Update repo version

0.33 -- Thu Jan 23 22:33:34 AST 2025

    [Significant updates since 0.31]
    - Updates for openssl 1.0 versions
    - Merged a minor Fedora patch for the Change log for correct UTF-8 names
    - Ah the good old days when SHA1 was good enough :-). RHEL, Fedora, SUSE
    - etc. have more secure configurations so many of the digests and curves
    - tested would fail - So test only a reduced set (based on Fedora 42+)

    [Change Log]
    - c1c525e Test for a reduced subset of digests and curves reflecting newer congigurations
    - 8fa0449 v0.32

